- Personal projects, achievements, and portfolio items
- Profile images, logos, and personal branding
- Any content in: src/data/portfolioData.js

RESTRICTIONS:
1. You may NOT use, copy, publish, or redistribute the protected personal data
2. You may NOT impersonate or misrepresent yourself as Kosmas Temperekidis
3. You may NOT use the personal data for any commercial or non-commercial purpose

PERMITTED USE:
- You MAY use this repository as a template for your own portfolio
- You MUST replace ALL personal data with your own information before deployment
- You MUST remove or replace all protected content listed above

